hof.net.userMessages

Class LevelInfoMessage

  • java.lang.Object
    • hof.net.userMessages.AbstractMessage
      • hof.net.userMessages.LevelInfoMessage

  • public class LevelInfoMessage
extends hof.net.userMessages.AbstractMessage
    This message shows that a level has finished or has started.
    It also contains information about any received Medals or if this was last level.
